====Usage notes====
* In Finnish spelling, all compounds are spelled as [[closed compound]]s or [[hyphenated compounds]], so the term yhdyssana is often erroneously used to only refer to closed or hyphenated compounds in English, and the term {{m|fi|sanaliitto}} (whose correct meaning is [[phrase]], [[set phrase]], or [[fixed phrase]]) is often erroneously used to refer to English [[open compound]]s.
* In Finnish spelling, compounds will be hyphenated under certain conditions (see [[-#Finnish|the rules described here]]).
